<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=983">everquest.allakhazam.com/...?quest=983</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
<br>
You already have the blood wolf harness.<br>
<br>
1) Go into Crystal Caverns and kill orcs till you get a bottle of Carsinic Acid...<br>
<br>
2) Find a dwarf named Erdarf Restil in one of the MANY bars in Thurgadin, and hand him the acid.. he will give you the Gem of Persuasion.<br>
<br>
3) Find Vores the Hunter in Great Divide and give him both the Harness and the Gem and he will give you the &quot;Control Harness&quot;<br>
<br>
The Control Harness is what you need..<br>
<br>
Then just wait in the room where the Broodmother spawns.  (Like I said, she is near an 8 hour spawn).  She is in the empty room (empty till she spawns) near the 2 guardian wurm spawn room in the caves in Great Divide.<br>
<br>
She is indifferent to everyone.<br>
<br>
hand her the harness, and she will start walking to the Giant Fort..<br>
<br>
At the same time 2 named giants at the fort will walk outside the gate<br>
<br>
(it is important to make sure that no one is fighting the giants at the fort when you do the trade, because if these giants are pulled at any time durring the quest it will fail).<br>
<br>
When the Broodmother attacks one of the giants, Fergul will DESPAWN.. and immediatly respawn and start running to the zone to EW.<br>
<br>
When he does snare him and kill him.  Loot the Legs. <p><table width="85%" border="0">
